title: The Programmer Cat
content: Programmers are like cats; they always start in the wrong place!

title: Null Pointer Exception Pool
content: Why can't programmers swim? Because every time they go into the water, they say: 'null pointer exception!'

title: Late Night Debugging
content: What makes a good programmer? Someone who codes late into the night and debugs it the next morning!

title: 404 Water Not Found
content: A programmer walks into a restaurant and orders 'a glass of water.' The waiter comes back and says: 'HTTP 404: Water not found!'

title: Tea with Error 500
content: Why do programmers always buy two cups of tea? Because they know one of them will give a 500 error!

title: Morning Bug Hunt
content: What does a programmer say when they wake up? 'I think I found a bug in my code!'

title: Happy Code Moment
content: How can you make a programmer happy? Give them a line of code that works!
